            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Sorry, something went wrong. Please try again later.</p>
            <a href="/" class="mt-6 inline-block bg-blue-500 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded hover:bg-blue-600 transition">
                Go Back Home
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

